  <entry>
    <title>Markdown语法笔记</title>
    <url>/2018/12/27/markdown/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>在这里简单记下 MD 的语法以备后续使用</p>
<blockquote>
<p>2020/03/31 根据 <span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9zcGVjLmNvbW1vbm1hcmsub3JnLzAuMjkv">CommonMark Spec 0.29<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span> 更新</p>
</blockquote>
<a id="more"></a>

<hr>
<ol>
<li>换行<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">换行</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">换行</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

</li>
</ol>
<p>解析为 <code>&lt;p&gt;强制&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;换行&lt;/p&gt;</code></p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">硬\</span><br><span class="line">换行</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>解析为 <code>&lt;p&gt;硬&lt;br /&gt;换行&lt;/p&gt;</code></p>
<hr>
<ol start="2">
<li>多级标题</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">一级标题</span><br><span class="line">=</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">二级标题</span><br><span class="line">-</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"># 一级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## 二级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">### 三级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">#### 四级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">##### 五级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">###### 六级标题</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>标题最多六级</p>
<hr>
<ol start="3">
<li>字体样式</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">_这是倾斜的文字_</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*这是倾斜的文字*</span>  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**这是加粗的文字**</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">__这是加粗的文字__</span>  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">***这是斜体加粗的文字**</span>*  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">___这是斜体加粗的文字__</span>_</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<ol start="4">
<li>引用</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; 引用内容</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; &gt; [*斜体引用链接*](超链接地址 "title")</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; &gt; ***</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; *斜体引用*</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<ol start="5">
<li>分割线</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">***</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">___</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<ol start="6">
<li>链接</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">*斜体显示名*</span>](<span class="link">/链接地址 "title"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">显示名</span>](<span class="link">/图片地址 "title"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">链接地址</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">参考链接名</span>]: <span class="link">/链接地址 "title"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>参考链接是不可见的</p>
<hr>
<ol start="7">
<li>列表</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>列表内容</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>列表内容</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+ </span>列表内容</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1. </span>列表内容</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2. </span>列表内容</span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">```markdown</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">```markdown</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">1) 列表内容</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">2) 列表内容</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">4. </span>列表内容</span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    1. 列表内容</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    - `列表代码内容`</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    - ***</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<ol start="8">
<li>代码块</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="code">`单行代码`</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="code">````语言名称</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">多行代码</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">  以及缩进</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">```语言名称</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">代码块内代码块</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">  以及缩进</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">```</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">````</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<pre><code>使用四个空格的代码块
  以及缩进</code></pre><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">~~~语言名称</span><br><span class="line">多行代码</span><br><span class="line">~~~</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<ol start="9">
<li>HTML</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">HTML</span> 标签&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
]]></content>
